metadata.name: Brainstorm #1/30
metadata.description:
*acrylic paint on canvas*

"Brainstorm" was painted immediately after after inspiration of seeing recent images of nebulas (star nurseries) that exist in our universe, at a nearby domed planetarium. I believe as a collective consciousness we can utilize our own 'brain power' , and generate ideas to empower us all to live a life that we are thriving in.
